  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b9c\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0ba8\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc2\u0bb1\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "May another Black July develop - Nalin Bandara prediction",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The people of the country are very angry with the government and the Rajapaksas. Decisions made by impatient people are likely to lead to another Black July.",
        "United People's Freedom Alliance (UPFA) MP Nalin Bandara has urged the government not to allow such a situation.",
        "He was speaking at a press conference held at the office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo on Tuesday (28).",
        "Kottapaya Rajapaksa is the curse of the country. The curse on the country will be lifted only if he resigns. The government is currently stating how to live inside the well.",
        "But that is not what people need. The expectation of the people is to get out of the well. For that, the Gotabhaya-led government must step down and hold elections. If not, an all-party government should be formed.",
        "One and a half months have passed since Ranil Wickremesinghe took office as Prime Minister, but no international assistance has been forthcoming.",
        "People are impatient. They are not in a position to obey even the religious leaders. Are furious with the rulers.",
        "It is impossible to say what decision people will make next. The situation is likely to be reported as Black July next month. We urge the government not to allow this to happen.",
        "The Rajapaksas who bankrupted the country in this way should be severely punished. But Ranil Wickremesinghe will not do that. This government has not even learned the lesson from the events of May 9.",
        "All opposition parties must work together to oust these rulers. Middle Eastern countries are not friendly with Sri Lanka. It needs to be updated again. He said this government does not have the capacity to do that."
      ],
